00:00:27.990 --> 00:00:32.659
This is the story of the 1998 article in the medical journal The

00:00:32.659 --> 00:00:38.050
Lancet, which made a link between a common vaccine and autism, and

00:00:38.250 --> 00:00:42.460
how its effects continue to be felt around the world to this very day.

